<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink387">
<l>aṟampuri yarumaṟai naviṉṟa nāviṟ</l>
<l>ṟiṟampuri koḷkai yantaṇir toḻuvaleṉ</l>
<l>ṟoṇṭoṭi viṉavum pētaiyam peṇṭē</l>
<l>kaṇṭaṉe mamma curattiṭai yavaḷai</l>
<l>yiṉṟuṇai yiṉitupā rāṭṭak</l>
<l>kuṉṟuyar piṟaṅkaṉ malaiyiṟan tōḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O naïve woman, who said: "I worship [you], </l>
<l>brahmins of principles that make [you] strong,  </l>
<l>whose tongues recite the precious Vedas, establishing virtue!”</l>
<l>and asked about [the girl] in bright bracelets! </l>
<l>We have seen her in the middle of the desert.</l>
<l>She traversed the glistening mountain with high peaks, </l>
<l>as her pleasant companion sweetly praised [her].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
